a big black bear

00:00:18.973 --> 00:00:21.209 position:5% line:83% align:start
and the big black bear
bled black blood.

00:00:21.310 --> 00:00:23.346 position:5% line:83% align:start
Cedar Shingles should
be shaved and saved.

00:00:23.446 --> 00:00:25.882 position:5% line:83% align:start
Don't doubt the doorbell,
but differ with the doorknob.

